                      #####################################
                      FFE Setup on Linux, MacOS and Windows
                      #####################################

          On Linux and MacOS, either FFESetup*.sh or FFESetup*.csh
          must be invoked in order to set environment variables needed
          to run Force Field Explorer from the command line. Note the
          scripts can either be "sourced" or run directly. On Windows,
          the FFESetupWin.bat script must be invoked prior to running
          FFE by double-clicking the app to achieve the same effect.

